channel.title: Server wont connect?
channel.description: I got a new server base, and I went i try to log into it after I hook in my ip, I did not see a spot where to put in my port in the client.java. I hooked in my ip from no-ip But it says Cannot connect to server, try a different world? Can anyone give me a tip on how to log into the server. There is one spot but when I put the port it tells me illegal start of type private static, so I guess that doesn't work.. since it doesn't accept my port.
